     *
     * @function Phaser.Geom.Polygon.Perimeter
     * @since 3.12.0
     *
     * @param {Phaser.Geom.Polygon} polygon - The Polygon to get the perimeter of.
     *
     * @return {number} The perimeter of the Polygon.
